text: Olagbegi Atanneye II was a paramount ruler of Owo Kingdom, Ondo state, southwestern Nigeria and the father of Olagbegi Atanneye I and Olowo Ajike Ogunoye. ==References== Category:Yoruba monarchs Category:Nigerian traditional rulers Category:People from Owo Category:Olagbegi family
title: Olagbegi Atanneye II
